{"tid":2139005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華借美法院過橋 追緝海外逃犯","createTime":"2020-08-04T04:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T04:12:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"44eb6e8cd17decdb9baa643bb4fe74c64a23991f","tid":2139005,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200804/YIBPEDCJGIYKMUDVJFOZU52HYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200804%2FYIBPEDCJGIYKMUDVJFOZU52HYM%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd6e24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=d213fb25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200804%2FYIBPEDCJGIYKMUDVJFOZU52HYM%2F&h=f55f6e13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200804/YIBPEDCJGIYKMUDVJFOZU52HYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華借美法院過橋 追緝海外逃犯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NsCiyJpm35OEEHeRdR-mQ4g04oM=/190x121/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HSJKKH5IDNDRPQBWI77SKJNQAU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNsCiyJpm35OEEHeRdR-mQ4g04oM%3D%2F190x121%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHSJKKH5IDNDRPQBWI77SKJNQAU.gif&h=1419b23f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京透過異地起訴，迫使逃犯返國受審。<br />\n<br />\n中國「獵狐行動」新手法曝光。繼扣押家人脅迫、恐嚇外，美媒報道，中國緝捕海外逃犯的新工具，正是美國法院。據報，中國2018年點名23名外逃官員或企業高層，指他們身處美國，當中至少六人正面對或曾面對中方在美國提出的民事訴訟， 有人被起訴後即回國。有美國法律專家指出，雖然做法未違反美國法律，但故意繞過正常外交和司法途徑，此舉動實際上是繞過了美國法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提民事訴訟逼返國<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。，將父女二人列為共同被告。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。但在訴訟提出約一個月後，肖建明突然返回中國。比較特別的是肖建明啟程前幾天，雲南錫業申請撤銷案件，但未有交代原因。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。，但事實是打擊海外華人，包括美國華人的反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》"}]}